*   ## **_SURPRISE PARTNER NATALYA, ZELINA VEGA AND LYRA VAKYRIA DEF. PURE FUSION COLLECTIVE_**
    

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/ff44f0f1-d6d0-43e8-b45c-dc148a296fcf/20240909_190632.jpg)

Drew McIntyre is out to cut a promo about how Punk touching some corners and claiming to have a victory over him is false. But it doesn't matter now because he beat Punk down and he'll never have to see him again.

Adam Pearce comes out and says he's spoken to CM Punk and they've agreed. Drew and Punk, Hell in a Cell.

